        "content": "<p>It would be really useful to pipe to <code>dbg</code> and have it return the value so we can inspect in the middle of a list of operations.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>[1, 2, 3]\n|&gt; List.map foo\n|&gt; dbg\n|&gt; List.sum\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Elixir has this feature.</p>",
        "id": 406606216,
        "sender_full_name": "Ryan Bates",
        "timestamp": 1701976692
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yep that is a planned feature</p>",
